fields.name: Notes:
fields.value:
Flex can literally be any sub-DPS or shielder, such as Fischl, Yelan, Jean, Layla and Diona.

Wanderer does want Faruzan (better at C6) or Jean (at C4+). However, Furina with a full-party healer can be better than a low constellation Faruzan.
